	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Valde sollicitus fui de remittendis epistolis, quas nuper miseras, nec ulla se captandam praebuit commoda occasio, cuius beneficio istuc possem; tandem forte fortuna nudius tertius advenit <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p8109" cert="high">Ioannes ab Ulmis</persName>, affinis meus, qui sancte se curaturum recepit, ut eę ad te bona fide perferantur.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Eo vero die <persName ref="p8371" cert="high">Albertus</persName>, meus ex fratre nepos, ad patrem scripsit inter cętera: "Deducetur ad nos <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2100" cert="high">Bipontum</placeName> sub finem mensis huius (septembris intellige) <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2481" cert="high">Svevię</placeName> regina, quam <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p20333" cert="high">Georgius Ioannes Palatinus</persName>, illustrissimi nostri <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p18405" cert="high">Wolfgangi</persName> patruelis, in uxorem ducet.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Inter hosce nostros et electorem <persName ref="p17927" cert="high">Palatinum</persName>, religionis excepto negocio, cęteris in rebus non male convenit; viget enim adhuc de dominicę cenę administratione controversia, cuiusque supra memini, <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p20333" cert="high">Georgius Iohannes</persName> eiusdem cum electore est sententiae."</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Hactenus nepos.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Bene vale, colendissime Bullingere, meque ama et Christo Iesu commenda.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">27. octobris 1563.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">T[uus] <persName ref="p8055" cert="high">A[mbrosius] Bl[aurerus]</persName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Ir werdt wissen, wie der <persName type="citizen_name">von Gruͦnbach</persName> <placeName ref="l1030" cert="high">Wirtzburg</placeName> mitt 500 pferden und 3 fendlin zuͦ fuͦß ingenommen und der bischoff die flucht in das schlosß genommen, item das hertzog <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p18716">Erich von Brunschwig Bomberg</persName> ingenomen, ouch <placeName ref="l361" cert="high">Nürenberg</placeName>, <placeName ref="l1976" cert="high">Augspurg</placeName>, <placeName ref="l513" cert="high">Ulm</placeName> etc. knecht annemmend, und sollend die Sachsischen fürsten mitt grossem volck heruß ziechen; nitt weist man, wider wen es ist.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Ettlich sagend, es seye wider den pfaltzgraffen churfursten von sines gloubens wegen.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Clarissimo d. Bullingero suo.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Zürich.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
		</body>
	</text>
